lead_paragraph: According to TiqIQ, a company that aggregates prices on the secondary market, tickets for Mets games at Citi Field seem to be more in demand at the moment than games at Yankee Stadium.

headline.main: Hotter Baseball Ticket in New York Is to See the Mets, It Appears
